    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concluded that the package meets the minimum documentation threshold for submission. NOTE: This acceptance decision is undermined by model version drift. The sole ValidationResult (hemolysis-absolute-vr-01) was generated by ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-24-build-2024q3 carrying modelVersion 2024-q3-build-2, whereas the UofA declares currentModelVersion 2026-q1-build-7. The hemolysis model coefficient set and discretization scheme were revised between these builds. The validation evidence therefore does not apply to the model of record, and the acceptance outcome should be treated as unsupported pending re-execution under build 2026-q1-build-7.",
